name: multiversedot0033
description: The lonely astronaut takes a moment of rest by sending himself adrift. In his mind his amateur self composed country songs are playing on repeat. Agdluak, the Karnimata traveling in his brain can barely stand to listen to them any longer. What their frustration will drive them to do is going to change the entire universe. - Snippet from the story line of one Dr. Prof. Kazimierz Maupa. We are not alone. Duh.
